section.def:
publish
                (發表) includes broadcast and otherwise
            disseminate;

subparagraph.content:
the conduct of the course or the part thereof, as the case may be, in
                        the premises will not expose any person in the premises to any undue risk of
                        fire;

the means of escape in case of fire available to persons in the
                        premises at any time when the course or the part thereof, as the case may
                        be, is to be conducted will be adequate;

paragraph.content:
any premises which are specified to the effect that they are designed and
                    constructed for educational purposes on a plan approved for the purposes of
                        section 14(1) of the Buildings Ordinance (Cap. 123);
